;</p><p>191.96.249.53 - - [23/Dec/2016:13:15:17 +0800] &quot;POST /xmlrpc.php HTTP/1.0&quot; 200 596 &quot;-&quot; &quot;Mozilla/4.0 (compatible: MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.0)&quot;</p><p>191.96.249.53 - - [23/Dec/2016:13:14:49 +0800] &quot;POST /xmlrpc.php HTTP/1.0&quot; 200 596 &quot;-&quot; &quot;Mozilla/4.0 (compatible: MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.0)&quot;</p><p>191.96.249.53 - - [23/Dec/2016:13:15:08 +0800] &quot;POST /xmlrpc.php HTTP/1.0&quot; 200 596 &quot;-&quot; &quot;Mozilla/4.0 (compatible: MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.0)&quot;</p><p>191.96.249.53 - - [23/Dec/2016:13:15:19 +0800] &quot;POST /xmlrpc.php HTTP/1.0&quot; 200 596 &quot;-&quot; &quot;Mozilla/4.0 (compatible: MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 6.0)&quot;</p><p><br/></p><p>木有办法，我只有搞个防火墙过滤一下ip。iptable一开始还搞错了，弄成所有人都不可访问了，直到重启云主机才恢复。/etc/iptables/rules.v4（手动创建）设置如下：</p><pre class=\"brush:bash;toolbar:false\">*filter\r\n-A&nbsp;INPUT&nbsp;-s&nbsp;191.96.249.53/24&nbsp;-p&nbsp;tcp&nbsp;--dport&nbsp;80&nbsp;-j&nbsp;DROP\r\nCOMMIT</pre><p>加载iptables生效</p><p>sudo iptables-restore &lt; /etc/iptables/rules.v4</p>','这破博客竟然有人来恶意攻击','','publish','open','open','','%e8%bf%99%e7%a0%b4%e5%8d%9a%e5%ae%a2%e7%ab%9f%e7%84%b6%e6%9c%89%e4%ba%ba%e6%9d%a5%e6%81%b6%e6%84%8f%e6%94%bb%e5%87%bb','','','2016-12-23 13:47:46','2016-12-23 05:47:46','',0,'http://nubi.me/?p=154',0,'post','',0),(18,1,'2015-10-12 11:41:12','2015-10-12 03:41:12','yum install scons\r\n\r\nwget http://fossies.org/linux/www/serf-1.3.8.tar.gz\r\n\r\ntar zvxf serf-1.3.8.tar.gz\r\n\r\ncd serf\r\n\r\nscons APR=/usr/local/apr/ APU=/usr/local/apr/\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n./configure --with-apr=/usr/local/apr/ --with-apr-util=/usr/local/apr-util/  --with-serf=/usr/local/\r\n\r\nmake\r\n\r\nmake install','centos6 编译subversion1.9.2版本','','publish','open','open','','centos6-%e7%bc%96%e8%af%91subversion1-9%e7%89%88%e6%9c%ac','','','2015-10-12 15:42:31','2015-10-12 07:42:31','',0,'http://nubi.me/?p=18',0,'post','',124),(19,1,'2015-10-12 11:41:12','2015-10-12 03:41:12','./configure --with-apr=/usr