ockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\"></embed>','CppCon 2015: Emacs as a C++ IDE','','inherit','closed','closed','','25-revision-v1','','','2015-11-06 12:02:37','2015-11-06 04:02:37','',25,'http://nubi.me/2015/11/06/25-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(30,1,'2015-11-06 12:08:55','2015-11-06 04:08:55','<embed src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XMTM3ODg0NTI5Mg==/v.swf\" allowFullScreen=\"true\"  type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\"></embed>','CppCon 2015: Emacs as a C++ IDE','','inherit','closed','closed','','25-revision-v1','','','2015-11-06 12:08:55','2015-11-06 04:08:55','',25,'http://nubi.me/2015/11/06/25-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2015-11-09 09:55:09','2015-11-09 01:55:09','1、通过apt-get安装adb\r\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:nilarimogard/webupd8\r\nsudo apt-get update\r\nsudo apt-get install android-tools-adb\r\n将android设备连接至电脑，执行adb shell会提示“error: device not found”\r\n\r\n2、将android设备连接至电脑，通过lsusb查看usb设备，如下红色部分对应的就是android设备\r\nBus 001 Device 001: ID 1d6b:0002 Linux Foundation 2.0 root hub\r\nBus 002 Device 001: ID 1d6b:0002 Linux Foundation 2.0 root hub\r\nBus 001 Device 002: ID 8087:0024 Intel Corp. Integrated Rate Matching Hub\r\nBus 002 Device 002: ID 8087:0024 Intel Corp. Integrated Rate Matching Hub\r\nBus 001 Device 027: ID 1f3a:1002\r\nBus 002 Device 003: ID 046d:c077 Logitech, Inc.\r\n\r\n3、创建adb_usb.ini文件，写入id\r\necho 0x1f3a > ~/.android/adb_usb.ini\r\n\r\n4、添加权限\r\nsudo vim /etc/udev/rules.d/70-android.rules\r\n加入以下内容，注意红色部分对应的就是lsusb得到的id\r\nSUBSYSTEM==\"usb\", ATTRS{idVendor}==\"1f3a\", ATTRS{idProduct}==\"1002\",MODE=\"0666\"\r\n\r\n5、重启USB服务\r\n$sudo chmod a+rx /etc/udev/rules.d/70-android.rules\r\n$sudo service udev restart\r\n\r\n6. 重启adb服务，adb devices有设备说明adb安装成功\r\n$adb kill-server\r\n$sudo adb start-server\r\n$adb devices\r\nList of devices attached\r\n815105148800601fe42     device\r\n','[转]Ubuntu12.04 安装adb','','publish','closed','closed','','%e8%bd%acubuntu-%e4%b8%8b%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%ae%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8android-adb','','','2015-11-09 10:27:58','2015-11-09 02:27:58','',0,'http://nubi.me/?p=31',0,'post','',0),(33,1,'2015-11-09 10:27:58','2015-11-09 02:27:58','1、通过apt-get安装adb\r\nsudo add-apt-repository ppa:nilarimogard/webupd8\r\nsudo apt-get update\r\nsudo apt-get install android-tools-adb\r\n将android设备连接至电脑，执行adb shell会提示“error: device not found”\r\n\r\n2、将android设备连接至电脑，通过lsusb查看usb设备，如下红色部分对应的就是android设备\r\nBus 001 Device 001: ID 1d6b:0002 Linux Foundation 2.0 root hub\r\nBus 002 Device 001: ID 1d6b:0002 Linux Foundation 2.0 root hub\r\nBus 001 Device 002: ID 8087:0024 Intel Corp. Integrated Rate Matching Hub\r\nBus 002 Device 002: ID 8087:0024 Intel Corp. Integrated Rate Matching Hub\r\nBus 001 Device 027: ID 1f3a:1002\r\nBus 002 Device 003: ID 046d:c077 Logitech, Inc.\r\n\r\n3、创建adb_usb.ini文件，写入id\r\necho 0x1f3a > ~/.android/adb_usb.ini\r\n\r\n4、添加权限\r\nsudo vim /etc/udev/rules.d/70-android.rules\r\n加入以下内容，注意红色部分对应的就是lsusb得到的id\r\nSUBSYSTEM==\"usb\", ATTRS{idVendor}==\"1f3a\", ATTRS{idProduct}==\"1002\",MODE=\"0666\"\r\n\r\n5、重启USB服务\r\n$sudo chmod a+rx /etc/udev/rules.d/70-android.rules\r\n$sudo service udev restart\r\n\r\n6. 重启adb服务，adb devices有设备说明adb安装成功\r\n$adb kill-server\r\n$sudo adb start-server\r\n$adb devices\r\nList of devices attached\r\n815105148800601fe42     device\r\n','[转]Ubuntu12.04 安装adb','','inherit','closed','closed','','31-revision-v1','','','2015-11-09 10:27:58','2015-11-09 02:27:58','',31,'http://nubi.me/2015/11/09/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(32,1,'2015-11-09 09:55:09','2015-11-09 01:55:09','1、配置环境变量\r\n\r\n进入终端，输入\r\n\r\nsudo gedit ~/.bashrc\r\n\r\n在文件的最后追加：\r\n\r\n?\r\n1\r\n2\r\n3\r\n#set path for android sdk tools\r\nexport PATH=$PATH:/your_android-sdk-linux_path/tools/\r\nexport PATH=$PATH:/your_android-sdk-linux_path/platform-tools/\r\n这里的your_android-sdk-linux_path是绝对路径\r\n\r\n2、保存后，同步更新\r\n\r\nsource ~/.bashrc\r\n\r\n3、如果直接运行adb之后，显示\r\n\r\nadb devices\r\n* daemon not running. starting it now *\r\n* daemon started successfully *\r\nList of devices attached\r\n???????????? no permissions\r\n\r\n没有权限\r\n\r\n\r\n4、切换到root，再次运行步骤1和2.\r\n\r\n然后重启adb服务\r\n\r\nadb kill-server\r\nadb start-server\r\n\r\n这样离开root后，也是可以使用adb的。\r\n\r\n5. 如果到运行步骤3，还是不行的话，参考以下方法：\r\n\r\n（1）插上手机，终端输入：\r\nlsusb\r\n\r\n会列出所有占用usb设备。\r\n从中找出你自己的设备：\r\n\r\nBus 002 Device 004: ID 17ef:6019 Lenovo \r\nBus 002 Device 003: ID 04c5: 1356 Fujitsu, Ltd                <--------这是我的设备。记下这一行。 \r\nBus 002 Device 002: ID 8087:0024   \r\nBus 002 Device 001: ID 1d6b:0002 Linux Foundation 2.0 root hub \r\nBus 001 Device 002: ID 8087:0024   \r\nBus 001 Device 001: ID 1d6b:0002 Linux Foundation 2.0 root hub \r\n\r\n（2）继续终端输入 \r\nsudo gedit /etc/udev/rules.d/70-android.rules \r\n\r\n加入如下语句 \r\nSUBSYSTEM==\"usb\", ATTRS{idVendor}==\" 04c5\", ATTRS{idProduct}==\" 1356\",MODE=\"0666\" \r\n（红色和绿色的字就是上面我们记下来的，分别对应）\r\n\r\n保存。\r\n\r\n（3）终端输入\r\nsudo chmod a+rx /etc/udev/rules.d/70-android.rules\r\nsudo service udev restart\r\n\r\n（4）拔掉usb，重新连上(很重要)，再执行：\r\nadb devices\r\n这样应该就能看设备.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n或者尝试以下方式：\r\n\r\n1、  Lsusb，找到本设备对应的vid。\r\n\r\n2、  打开或者新建 ~/.android/adb_usb.ini文 件。\r\n\r\n3、  将vid写入文件。重新adb kill-server或者adb start-server。\r\n','[转]Ubuntu 下配置使用Android adb','','inherit','closed','closed','','31-revision-v1','','','2015-11-09 09:55:09','2015-11-09 01:55:09','',31,'http://nubi.me/2015/11/09/31-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(40,1,'2015-11-13 23:40:25','2015-11-13 15:40:25','jhizdfncqhdjhizdfncqhdjhizdfncqhdjhizdfncqhdjhizdfncqhd','jhizdfncqhd','','inherit','closed','closed','','39-revision-v1','','','2015-11-13 23:40:25','2015-11-13 15:40:25','',39,'http://nubi.me/2015/11/13/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(41,1,'2015-11-15 15:02:34','2015-11-15 07:02:34','以前可以在32位系统运行的，害得我重装里系统哈','Linux版Dota2现在只支持64位系统了','','inherit','closed','closed','','39-revision-v1','','','2015-11-15 15:02:34','2015-11-15 07:02:34','',39,'http://nubi.me/2015/11/15/39-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0)