ont-family:Consolas; font-size:10pt\">    $ sudo bin/csvn-httpd install</span></p></li></ol>','CollabNet SubversionEdge安装教程','','inherit','closed','closed','','127-revision-v1','','','2016-08-04 10:24:04','2016-08-04 02:24:04','',127,'http://nubi.me/2016/08/04/127-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(131,1,'2016-08-04 10:32:01','2016-08-04 02:32:01','<p> \n </p><h2><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">requirements \n</span></h2><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">git 1.8 \n</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">jdk 1.8 \n</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">centos 6 \n</span></li></ul><h2><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">安装过程 \n</span></h2><ol><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">选择安装目录<br/></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">这里放在/home/git目录下<br/><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">mkdir /home/git<br/>cd /home/git </span>\n			</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">解压安装包<br/></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">tar zvxf atlassian-bitbucket-4.4.1.tar.gz </span>\n			</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">修改git库目录，就是保存代码库的目录，我这里设置为/home/git/rep-home<br/></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">cd atlassian-bitbucket-4.4.1/bin/<br/>vim setenv.sh<br/>if [ \"x${BITBUCKET<sub>HOME</sub>}\" = \"x\" ]; then<br/>export BITBUCKET<sub>HOME</sub>=/home/git/rep-home<br/>fi </span>\n			</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">启动bitbucket<br/></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">./start-bitbucket.sh</span>\n			</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">打开浏览器，访问git服务器ip地址和7990端口，输入使用一个月的免费key，中间还要连接mysql数据什么的，自己搞定 \n</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">替换几个jar包，破解使用限制<br/></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt\">先停止bitbucket服务器<br/><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">./stop-bitbucket.sh<br/>cd</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Consolas\">jar</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">包所在的目录</span><spa